title: Sonic the Hedgehog 2006 - Silver's story
description:
Part 3 of 4. I&#039;ve checked for sync issues in this one and didn&#039;t see any, but there might still be some that I didn&#039;t pick up, but most likely not. This is Silver, the new hedgehog&#039;s story, you&#039;ll find that quite a few scenes are "shared" from other character stories you may have already downloaded, with minor differences, though some are just complete copies. I&#039;ve included them just in case you didn&#039;t download the other two stories.

This is the last character story, the final part will be the hidden last episode.  I&#039;ll include a fight with the final boss at the end as well.
